Nigerian singer, Innocent Idibia, popularly known as Tuface or 2Baba, has regretted losing so much precious time with his children which he could never get back. The singer expressed this via his Instagram story, while reacting to a video of Portuguese professional footballer, Cristiano Ronaldo. He wrote, “This has got me teary. “I have lost so many precious time with all my children and I can’t rewind. I am so sad about that, so this is a true wake up call for me as a father.” Recall that Tuface has seven children by three women, including his wife, Annie who has two daughters for him. His second baby mama, Sumbo Adeoye, who is now married to Pastor David Adeoye has two boys for him, while Pero has three kids comprising two boys and a girl for the Nigerian singer.